title: Starting out, LFT/G with other newer players
body:
not yet lvl 30, literally 5-6 pvp non-ranked games played, looking to play more and improve,  looking for club with people at a similar stage/maybe just hit 30.

Like to play jg/mid/supp, hope to get some new champs soon.

Proud Kiwi, cheers.

replies.body: hey sounds good to me... I would like to join.
